    <h3>ARIA : Navigation Role</h3>

    <p class="text-muted">Identify major groups of links used for navigation, using navigation landmark role(div with role=navigation or nav elements) for the page. More about the navigation role on <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/Navigation_Role">MDN Web Docs</a>.</p>
    {%  if collector.navigationElements is not empty %}
        <p>Found {{ collector.navigationElements|length }} navigation roles:</p>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Tag</th>
                    <th>Links</th>
                    <th>Aria label</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for navigation in collector.navigationElements %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ navigation.tag }}</td>
                        <td>
                            <ul>
                                {% for link in navigation.links %}
                                    <li>{{ link }}</li>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </ul>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                            {% if navigation.ariaLabel %}
                                {{ navigation.ariaLabel }}
                            {% else %}
                                <div class="card status-warning">
                                    <strong>Missing</strong>
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>
    {% else %}
